<div style="position:absolute;left:357.00px;top:781.20px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">我懂一點英語。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:89.40px;top:796.14px" class="cls_012"><span class="cls_012">えい  ご</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.20px;top:799.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">⑦</span><span class="cls_008"> </span><span class="cls_007">英語が</span><span class="cls_002">  </span><span class="cls_007">あまり</span><span class="cls_002">  </span><span class="cls_007">わかりません。</span></div>
